    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a collector-grade vehicle that represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows like a brand-new vehicle. The exterior paint retains its original factory depth and mirror-like clarity, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather remains supple and matte, lacking the typical shine of wear, and the carpets are protected by original, heavy-duty mats. All technology, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, operates with factory-fresh precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
